        - Bundle compliance\
\
Statistical Power:\
    - Sample size: 500 patients per group\
    - Expected effect size: 20% reduction in mortality\
    - Power: 80%\
    - Alpha: 0.05\
\
Duration:\
    - Minimum 6 months\
    - Review interim results monthly\
    - Early stopping rules for harm or overwhelming benefit\
```\
